# Gemini 2.5 Flash Live Preview

The Live API enables low-latency, real-time voice and video interactions with Gemini 2.5 Flash. It processes continuous streams of audio, video, or text to deliver immediate, human-like spoken responses, creating a natural conversational experience for your users.
[Try in Google AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com?model=gemini-2.5-flash-native-audio-preview-12-2025)

